即使考慮了秘書處的體型及構造，牠的步幅仍是很大<ref name="Mitchell-93-94"/>。在進行針對必利時錦標的訓練時，秘書處的步幅是24英尺11英寸<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.nytimes.com/1973/05/14/archives/fast-drill-time-for-secretariat-threeyearold-in-last-big-preakness.html |title = FAST DRILL TIME FOR SECRETARIAT |author = The New York Times |date = 1973-05-14 |publisher = The New York Times |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-15 |archive-date = 2018-06-15 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180615191848/https://www.nytimes.com/1973/05/14/archives/fast-drill-time-for-secretariat-threeyearold-in-last-big-preakness.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。秘書處強大的後軀令牠能夠釋放「壓倒性」的速度，而且牠肌肉發達及心臟容量較為強勁，使牠幾乎可以在任何比賽中於任何時候超越對手<ref name="Mitchell-93-94"/>。

在1973年3月29日，秘書處的體重是1,155磅（524公斤）<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.drf.com/news/secretariat-hatton-1973-season |title = Secretariat: Hatton on the 1973 season |author = Charles Hatton |date = 2012-03-08 |publisher = Daily Racing Form |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-15 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180615190940/http://www.drf.com/news/secretariat-hatton-1973-season |archivedate = 2018-06-15 }}</ref>。在完成三冠大賽後，秘書處的體重於6月15日僅下降了24磅至1131磅（513公斤）<ref name="DRF-DI@100923"/>。秘書處的食量很驚人，在準備三冠大賽期間牠每天需要進食15[[夸脫|夸脫]]的燕麥，而且為了防止脂肪增加，牠還需要非常努力地進行訓練才能保持健康<ref name="SI-WN@940919">{{Cite web |url = https://www.si.com/vault/1994/09/19/132047/17-secretariat |title = 17 SECRETARIAT |author = William Nack |date = 1994-09-19 |publisher = Sports Illustrated |language = en |accessdate = 2018-05-24 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180212083449/https://www.si.com/vault/1994/09/19/132047/17-secretariat |archivedate = 2018-02-12 }}</ref>。

於克萊伯恩農場工作的賽斯·漢考克（Seth Hancock）在接受《[[運動畫刊|運動畫刊]]》訪問時曾經表示：「如果秘書處是人類，牠會變成怎樣？試幻想，他將會是世界上最偉大的運動員。他擁有完美的身高，而且真正聰明及善良。最重要的是，他將會是有史以來最好看的人。他就是這些優點以馬匹之形集於一身。他甚至不再是一匹馬了。他是一個傳奇」<ref name="SI-WN@900604">{{Cite web |url = https://www.si.com/longform/belmont/ |title = Pure Heart |author = William Nack |date = 1990-06-04 |publisher = Sports Illustrated Longform |language = en |accessdate = 2018-05-24 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180528215255/https://www.si.com/longform/belmont/ |archivedate = 2018-05-28 }}</ref>。

==競賽生涯==
[[File:Owner_Meadow_Stable.svg|thumb]]
秘書處的參賽顏色及其騎師的綵衣顏色是以藍白方格為主。在比賽中，秘書處不會以繃帶綁腿，但牠通常會佩戴眼罩來集中精神<ref name="DRF-DI@100923"/>。秘書處雖然擁有跑手的體格，但是牠卻很彆扭及笨拙，導致牠經常被其他更早熟的馬匹超越，例如牠以26秒跑了四分之一英里，但其餘馬匹則以23秒跑畢<ref name="Nack p.66-67">Nack, pp. 66-67</ref>。秘書處的策騎員主要是由吉姆·高夫尼（Jim Gaffney）及查理·戴維斯（Charlie Davis）擔任。戴維斯最初並沒有對這匹馬留下深刻的印象，但他後來表示：「牠（秘書處）是一個大胖子。我的意思是牠很大。牠並不急於做任何事，牠自有計劃。而且牠不會輕易展示牠的質素給人看，除非牠想」<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.ocala.com/news/20100604/secretariats-exercise-rider-reflects-on-champion-horse |title = Secretariat’s exercise rider reflects on champion horse |author = Fred Hiers |date = 2010-06-04 |publisher = Ocala StarBanner |language = en |accessdate = 2018-05-25 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180525205948/http://www.ocala.com/news/20100604/secretariats-exercise-rider-reflects-on-champion-horse |archivedate = 2018-05-25 }}</ref>。高夫尼在接受訪問時憶起1972年首次策騎秘書處的事情，他更指出「從第一天起，我便知道牠（秘書處）有一股我從未感受過的力量」<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.newsday.com/long-island/obituaries/jim-gaffney-exercise-rider-for-secretariat-dead-at-75-1.1978626 |title = Jim Gaffney, exercise rider for Secretariat, dead at 75 |author = John Jeansonne |date = 2010-06-03 |publisher = Newsday |language = en |accessdate = 2018-05-25 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180525205000/https://www.newsday.com/long-island/obituaries/jim-gaffney-exercise-rider-for-secretariat-dead-at-75-1.1978626 |archivedate = 2018-05-25 }}</ref>。此外，馬伕埃迪·斯威特（Eddie Sweat）亦是秘書處團隊的其中一個重要成員，他主要照顧馬匹的起居飲食及進行日常護理工作。有一次，斯威特向記者表示：「我想馬伕比任何人都靠近馬匹。每天馬主及練馬師只會見牠（秘書處）一次，但我與牠一起生活一起工作」<ref>Scanlan, pp. 1-14</ref>。

呂西安·勞林會定期向潘妮·切納里匯報秘書處的狀況，更表示秘書處仍在學習如何跑步及需要減走嬰兒肥<ref name="Nack p.66-67"/><ref name="BH-JW@100922">{{Cite web |url = http://cs.bloodhorse.com/blogs/thoroughbred-bloggers-alliance/archive/2010/09/22/secretariat-the-beauty-of-being-everything.aspx |title = Secretariat: The Beauty of Being Everything. |author = Jennifer Wirth |date = 2010-09-22 |publisher = Blood-Horse |language = en |accessdate = 2018-05-26 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180526190224/http://cs.bloodhorse.com/blogs/thoroughbred-bloggers-alliance/archive/2010/09/22/secretariat-the-beauty-of-being-everything.aspx |archivedate = 2018-05-26 }}</ref>。切納里回想起在秘書處接受訓練時，勞林曾經說過：「妳那匹勇者帝王後裔並沒有向我展示牠的才能，牠甚至跑得比胖子慢」<ref name="LM-JM@0704">{{Cite web |url = https://www.loumag.com/articledisplay.aspx?id=37837893 |title = Stride for Stride with Big Red |author = Josh Moss |date = 2007-04 |publisher = Louisville Magazine |language = en |accessdate = 2018-05-26 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160820092248/https://www.loumag.com/articledisplay.aspx?id=37837893 |archivedate = 2016-08-20}}</ref>。但其後秘書處在春季取得穩定的進展。秘書處於6月6日首次佩戴眼罩，並以47⅗秒跑畢半[[英里|英里]]，其後牠更在同月24日以1分12⅘秒跑畢六[[化朗|化朗]]。最後，勞林致電切納里並告訴她秘書處已經準備好參加比賽<ref>Nack, pp. 77-78</ref>。

=== 1972年 ===
1972年7月4日，秘書處首次於{{tsl|en|Aqueduct Racetrack|雅佳特馬場}}亮相。在其中一場賽事中，某匹參賽馬在中途突然轉換跑道，引發了連鎖反應，秘書處亦因為被撞到而受到重創及退縮起來，最終秘書處獲得第四名<ref name="SI-WN@900604"/><ref>Woolfe, pp. 41-45</ref>。根據騎師保羅·費利西亞諾（Paul Feliciano）所言，若非秘書處的身體強壯，他有可能會墮馬。自此之後，秘書處便很少在比賽中出現退縮行為，而勞林則歸因於牠在首次比賽時被撞的經歷<ref name="SI-PP@730326">{{Cite web |url = https://www.si.com/vault/1973/03/26/567199/oh-lord-hes-perfect |title = Oh Lord, He's Perfect |author = Pat Putnam |date = 1973-03-26 |publisher = Sports Illustrated |language = en |accessdate = 2018-05-27 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180527201746/https://www.si.com/vault/1973/03/26/567199/oh-lord-hes-perfect |archivedate = 2018-05-27 }}</ref>。7月15日，費利西亞諾在康復後再度策騎秘書處，並拋離對手六個馬位勝出賽事<ref name="Woolfe">Woolfe, front end papers</ref>。7月31日，在{{tsl|en|Saratoga Race Course|沙拉托加馬場}}的一場比賽中，秘書處的騎師由費利西亞諾更換為羅恩·圖爾科特（Ron Turcotte）。在該場賽事中秘書處奪得冠軍，這引起了資深體育記者查爾斯·哈頓（Charles Hatton）的注意<ref>Woolfe, pp. 47-48</ref>。哈頓後來在報導中表示：「我從未看見過完美。我絕對沒辦法以任何形式指責牠或批評牠犯錯，其他人也沒可能，而這是一件令人驚嘆的事情。牠的身體、頭部和眼睛等等，簡直太不可思議了。坦白地說，我簡直不敢相信我的眼睛」<ref name="BH-JW@100922"/>。

8月，秘書處參加了{{tsl|en|Sanford Stakes|桑福德錦標}}，而這場賽事還有一匹備受矚目的競賽馬參賽。在比賽中途，秘書處被數匹競賽馬擋住前路，但之後牠像「一隻鷹在驅散一群小雞」般突圍而出，並最終拋離對手三個馬位勝出賽事<ref name="DRF-CH@120803"/>。體育記者安德魯·貝葉爾（Andrew Beyer）於報章{{tsl|en|The Washington Star|華盛頓之星}}報導了這場比賽，後來更表示：「我從未看過一匹能輕鬆地勝出賽事的兩歲馬，牠的潛力很大」<ref name="WP-AB@101007">{{Cite web |url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2010/10/07/AR2010100700237.html?noredirect=on |title = 'Secretariat' introduces extraordinary horse to a new generation |author = Andrew Beyer |date = 2010-10-07 |publisher = Washington Post |language = en |accessdate = 2018-05-28 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180528215623/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2010/10/07/AR2010100700237.html?noredirect=on |archivedate = 2018-05-28 }}</ref>。在十日後的{{tsl|en|Hopeful Stakes|希望錦標 (美國)|希望錦標}}中，秘書處作出了一個眩目的舉動，牠在¼英里內先後超越八匹競賽馬並成為領頭馬匹，最終以1分16⅕秒且拋離對手五個馬位勝出賽事<ref name="NC-PK@150906">{{Cite web |url = http://numerocinqmagazine.com/2015/09/06/secretariat-a-personal-memoir-patrick-j-keane/ |title = Secretariat: A Personal Memoir |author = Patrick J. Keane |date = 2015-09-06 |publisher = Numéro Cinq |language = en |accessdate = 2018-05-30 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170616232726/http://numerocinqmagazine.com/2015/09/06/secretariat-a-personal-memoir-patrick-j-keane/ |archivedate = 2017-06-16 }}</ref><ref>Woolfe, p. 51</ref>。

10月14日，秘書處參加了於貝蒙舉行的{{tsl|en|Champagne Stakes (United States)|香檳錦標}}<ref name="Woolfe"/>。在這場賽事中，秘書處在初段跑得較慢並在轉彎時作出較大動作，最終以兩個馬位勝出，但賽後經過評審調查後，秘書處被認為干擾了其他馬匹，因此牠被貶為第二名<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=82xkAAAAIBAJ&sjid=GX0NAAAAIBAJ&pg=2477,2912731&dq=secretariat+champagne-stakes&hl=en |title = Stop the Music wins disqualification |author = Calgary Herald |date = 1972-10-16 |publisher = Canadian Press |language = en |accessdate = 2018-05-30 |archive-date = 2020-04-20 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200420225639/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=82xkAAAAIBAJ&sjid=GX0NAAAAIBAJ&pg=2477%2C2912731&dq=secretariat+champagne-stakes&hl=en |dead-url = no }}</ref>。10月28日，秘書處在{{tsl|en|Laurel Futurity Stakes|桂冠未來錦標}}中以八個馬位勝出賽事<ref>Woolfe, pp. 58-59</ref>。

11月18日，秘書處在完成{{tsl|en|Garden State Stakes|花園州錦標}}後便結束1972年賽季<ref name="SI-WT@721127"/>。勞林其後接受訪問表示秘書處的表現讓他有很深刻的印象，因為牠在起跑時總是墊底，需要時間才能追趕上其他馬匹，又指出一匹馬駒若想成為真正的跑手就必須懂得擺脫困境<ref name="SI-WT@721127">{{Cite web |url = https://www.si.com/vault/1972/11/27/619154/thorns-among-the-roses |title = Thorns among the roses |author = Whitney Tower |date = 1972-11-27 |publisher = Sports Illustrated |language = en |accessdate = 2018-05-30 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161010001946/http://www.si.com/vault/1972/11/27/619154/thorns-among-the-roses |archivedate = 2016-10-10 }}</ref>。

秘書處在這一年贏得兩項{{tsl|en|Eclipse Award|日蝕獎}}，包括{{tsl|en|American Champion Two-Year-Old Male Horse|美國最佳兩歲雄馬}}及{{tsl|en|American Horse of the Year|美國年度馬王}}<ref name="Bowen@p.17-18">Bowen, pp. 17-18</ref>，而{{tsl|en|National Thoroughbred Racing Association|北美純種賽馬協會}}及報章《{{tsl|en|Daily Racing Form|每日賽馬態況}}》更是有份於年度馬王評選中投票予秘書處<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://colinsghost.org/2010/01/la-prevoyante-or-secretariat-horse-of-the-year-1972.html |title = La Prevoyante or Secretariat, Horse of the Year 1972 |author = Colin's Ghost |date = 2010-01-13 |language = en |accessdate = 2018-05-30 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180324224515/http://colinsghost.org/2010/01/la-prevoyante-or-secretariat-horse-of-the-year-1972.html |archivedate = 2018-03-24 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.nytimes.com/1972/12/27/archives/secretariat-is-horse-of-year-topping-la-prevoyante-in-poll.html |title = Secretariat Is Horse of Year, Topping La Prevoyante in Poll |author = Steve Cady |date = 1972-12-27 |publisher = The New York Times |language = en |accessdate = 2018-05-30 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180311152202/https://www.nytimes.com/1972/12/27/archives/secretariat-is-horse-of-year-topping-la-prevoyante-in-poll.html |archivedate = 2018-03-11 }}</ref>。自此之後，就只有{{tsl|en|Favorite Trick|拿手好戲}}在1997年以兩歲之齡奪得美國年度馬王獎項<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/155908/tricks-pic-reinforces-nick |title = Trick's Pic Reinforces Nick |author = Alan Porter |date = 2008-01-25 |publisher = Blood-Horse |language = en |accessdate = 2018-05-30 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180612142016/https://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/155908/tricks-pic-reinforces-nick |archivedate = 2018-06-12 }}</ref>。

=== 1973年 ===
1973年1月，克里斯托弗·切納里去世，龐大的遺產稅令潘妮·切納里承受很大負擔，她更一度考慮出售秘書處<ref name="NYTimes-RG@170917"/>。其後，潘妮·切納里聯同克萊伯恩農場的賽斯·漢考克（Seth Hancock）以團體馬匹名義出售秘書處的擁有權，並以每股價值190,000美元的價格售出32份股份，總值608萬美元<ref name="NYTimes@730227">{{Cite web |url = https://www.nytimes.com/1973/02/27/archives/secretariat-is-syndicated-for-record-608million.html?_r=0 |title = Secretariat Is Syndicated For Record $6.08‐Million |author = The New York Times |date = 1973-02-27 |publisher = The New York Times |language = en |accessdate = 2018-05-31 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161009192457/http://www.nytimes.com/1973/02/27/archives/secretariat-is-syndicated-for-record-608million.html?_r=0 |archivedate = 2016-10-09 }}</ref>。漢考克表示基於秘書處在兩歲時的表現以及牠的配種和外觀，令這次的股份銷售變得容易<ref name="NYTimes@730227"/>。潘妮·切納里保留了4份股份，並可以完全控制秘書處在三歲時的競賽活動，但需同意秘書處在1973年底退役<ref name="SI-PP@730326"/>。

秘書處在佛羅里達州過冬，但沒有參加賽事，直至3月17日牠才參加了{{tsl|en|Bay Shore Stakes|灣岸錦標}}。秘書處對手的練馬師曾經說過：「我們擁有的唯一機會就是牠（秘書處）摔倒了」<ref name="SI-PP@730326"/>。在賽事中，秘書處因其中一匹競賽馬試圖在馬群中突圍而出而被撞，但最後仍勝出。賽後，其中一位騎師聲稱秘書處犯規，但後來評審檢查競賽期間拍攝的照片，確定秘書處是被撞擊的一方而且沒有犯規，最終維持原本結果<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.nytimes.com/1973/03/18/archives/secretariat-wins-after-an-inquiry-smile-turns-to-frown-splitting.html |title = Secretariat Wins After an Inquiry |author = Joe Nichols |date = 1973-03-18 |publisher = The New York Times |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-16 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180616114117/https://www.nytimes.com/1973/03/18/archives/secretariat-wins-after-an-inquiry-smile-turns-to-frown-splitting.html |archivedate = 2018-06-16 }}</ref><ref>Capps, pp. 112-113</ref>。經歷灣岸錦標一役，秘書處的表現在冬季過後已經有所改善，而且牠還能應對逆境<ref name="BH-SH@130121">{{Cite web |url = http://cs.bloodhorse.com/blogs/horse-racing-steve-haskin/archive/2013/01/21/big-red-and-the-winter-of-73.aspx |title = Big Red and the Winter of '73 |author = Steve Haskin |date = 2013-01-21 |publisher = Blood-Horse |language = en |accessdate = 2018-05-31 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170920043026/http://cs.bloodhorse.com/blogs/horse-racing-steve-haskin/archive/2013/01/21/big-red-and-the-winter-of-73.aspx |archivedate = 2017-09-20 }}</ref>。

在4月7日舉行的{{tsl|en|Gotham Stakes|葛咸錦標}}內，由於沒有其他速度較快的競賽馬參加，勞林決定嘗試改變戰術，讓秘書處自行決定跑速<ref name="TRC-TC@150301">{{Cite web |url = https://www.thoroughbredracing.com/articles/looking-back-gothams-glorious-history/ |title = Looking back: The Gotham's glorious history |author = Terry Conway |date = 2015-03-01 |publisher = Thoroughbred Racing Commentary |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-01 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160322130913/https://www.thoroughbredracing.com/articles/looking-back-gothams-glorious-history |archivedate = 2016-03-22 }}</ref>。在賽事中，秘書處在起跑後已經領先，最後更拋離對手香檳查理（Champagne Charlie）三個馬位勝出<ref name="TRC-TC@150301"/><ref name="BH-SH@130121"/>。

在[[肯塔基打吡|肯塔基打吡]]舉行前，秘書處參加了{{tsl|en|Wood Memorial Stakes|伍德紀念錦標}}，並取得第三名<ref name="BH-SH@130121"/><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.kentuckyderby.com/history/moments/secretariat |title = 1973, Secretariat |author = Churchill Downs Incorporated |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-01 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180619100517/https://www.kentuckyderby.com/history/moments/secretariat |archivedate = 2018-06-19 }}</ref>。後來，勞林指出秘書處輸掉比賽的原因是牠口腔內出現膿腫，而這會導致馬匹出現不適<ref name="SI-WN@900604"/><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.secretariat.com/past-performances/wood-memorial/ |title = April 21, 1973 ~ Wood Memorial ~ 1 1/8 mile ~ Aqueduct Race Course |author = secretariat.com |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-01 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161230103225/http://www.secretariat.com/past-performances/wood-memorial/ |archivedate = 2016-12-30 }}</ref>。基於秘書處在伍德紀念錦標所取得的成績，傳媒開始猜測牠在肯塔基打吡能否取得佳績<ref>Capps, p. 121</ref>。有些人開始質疑秘書處的耐力，因為牠的身型是典型適合參加短途賽，而且牠的父親勇者帝王是以短跑聞名<ref name="SI-WN@900604"/>。另外更有傳言指秘書處的身體不健全<ref name="SI-WN@900604"/>。

==== 肯塔基打吡 ====
5月5日舉行的肯塔基打吡吸引了134,476人前往{{tsl|en|Churchill Downs|丘吉爾唐斯}}觀看，是北美賽馬史上入場人數最多的一屆<ref name="SI-WT@730514">{{Cite web |url = https://www.si.com/vault/1973/05/14/618031/it-was-murder |title = It was murder |author = Whitney Tower |date = 1973-05-14 |publisher = Sports Illustrated |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-02 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180212083416/https://www.si.com/vault/1973/05/14/618031/it-was-murder |archivedate = 2018-02-12 }}</ref>。在賽事中，次熱門馬匹{{tsl|en|Sham (horse)|Sham}}於內欄領先，而大熱門馬匹秘書處則位於較外的位置，但其後秘書處開始追上，並最終以2½個馬位勝出<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=xXwsAAAAIBAJ&sjid=1swEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6946,1218071&dq=secretariat+kentucky-derby&hl=en |title = Secretariat charges past Sham in Kentucky Derby win |author = Herald-Journal |date = 1973-05-06 |publisher = Associated Press |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-02 |archive-date = 2020-04-21 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200421183916/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=xXwsAAAAIBAJ&sjid=1swEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6946%2C1218071&dq=secretariat+kentucky-derby&hl=en |dead-url = no }}</ref>。秘書處在這場賽事中以1分59​⅖秒跑畢1¼英里，刷新了大賽紀錄<ref name="SI-WT@730514"/>。秘書處每跑¼英里路程，牠所需的時間都比之前更快，而每¼英里所需時間分別是25⅕秒、24秒、23⅘秒、23⅖秒及23秒<ref name="SI-WN@900604"/>。這意味著秘書處在跑最後¼英里路程時仍在加速<ref name="ACP-AH"/>。秘書處這項紀錄至今仍無人能破，直至2001年才有另一匹馬以1分59秒97完成賽事，是相隔二十多年來再有馬匹在2分鐘內勝出肯塔基打吡<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.nytimes.com/2001/05/06/sports/horse-racing-monarchos-makes-his-point-and-roars-to-victory-in-the-derby.html |title = HORSE RACING; Monarchos Makes His Point and Roars to Victory in the Derby |author = Joe Drape |date = 2001-05-06 |publisher = The New York Times |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-02 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160815070400/http://www.nytimes.com/2001/05/06/sports/horse-racing-monarchos-makes-his-point-and-roars-to-victory-in-the-derby.html |archivedate = 2016-08-15 }}</ref>。

體育記者邁克·沙利文（Mike Sullivan）後來說<ref>Sullivan, pp. 19-20</ref>：
{{quote|在1973年秘書處參加肯塔基打吡時我在場，那是……那只是美麗，你知道嗎？牠（秘書處）在起跑時墊底，而這只是牠的風格。當時我正在看第二位的馬匹Sham，你必須明白Sham是一匹很快及很漂亮的競賽馬，牠可能會在另一年取得三冠大賽冠軍，而且似乎沒有比Sham更快的馬。當每個人都看著Sham的時候，他們可能都是想像到這場比賽要結束了。但突然之間，有東西進入了你的視野之中。而當你還在確認它是什麼之前，秘書處已經來了，之後秘書處更超前了Sham。沒有人見過馬匹會有這樣的跑法，許多資深馬迷都說著同樣的事情。這就好像秘書處是另一種動物而不是馬匹一樣。}}

==== 必利時錦標 ====
[[File:Secretariat_in_Preakness_Stakes.jpg|thumb]]
5月19日，秘書處參加了於{{tsl|en|Pimlico Race Course|賓利高馬場}}舉行的[[必利時錦標|必利時錦標]]。在賽事中，秘書處起步較慢，但其後牠在不足¼英里的路程內超越其他馬匹並由最後一名成為領先者，雖然一度被追近，但牠最終仍以2½個馬位勝出<ref name="secretariat-BD">{{Cite web |url = https://www.secretariat.com/fan-club/writers-forum/the-day-time-didnt-stand-still/ |title = The Day Time Didn't Stand Still |author = Bill Doolittle |publisher = secretariat.com |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-03 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160829045752/http://www.secretariat.com/fan-club/writers-forum/the-day-time-didnt-stand-still/ |archivedate = 2016-08-29 }}</ref>。騎師羅恩·圖爾科特（Ron Turcotte）後來表示他為這次勝利感到自豪，因為他在即將轉第一個彎位時作出了一個決定：「我不想在轉彎時被困在馬群之中，所以我讓我的馬匹減速，讓其他馬匹超越我」<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.philly.com/philly/sports/20080605_Jockey_looks_back_at_Secretariat_s_1973_Triple_Crown.html |title = Jockey looks back at Secretariat's 1973 Triple Crown |author = Dick Jerardi |date = 2008-06-05 |publisher = The Philadelphia Inquirer |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-03 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180619100409/http://www.philly.com/philly/sports/20080605_Jockey_looks_back_at_Secretariat_s_1973_Triple_Crown.html |archivedate = 2018-06-19 }}</ref>。報章《每日賽馬態況》的攝影師雷蒙德·伍爾費（Raymond Woolfe）拍攝了秘書處在比賽中的跑姿，後來這張相片更成為了英國雕塑家約翰·史凱平（John Skeaping）設計秘書處雕像的基礎<ref name="BH-SH@120620">{{Cite web |url = http://cs.bloodhorse.com/blogs/horse-racing-steve-haskin/archive/2012/06/20/viva-big-red.aspx |title = Viva Big Red! |author = Steve Haskin |date = 2012-06-20 |publisher = Blood-Horse |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-03 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180407053453/http://cs.bloodhorse.com/blogs/horse-racing-steve-haskin/archive/2012/06/20/viva-big-red.aspx |archivedate = 2018-04-07 }}</ref>。

然而，秘書處的時間紀錄出現爭議。由於場內計時器出現故障，故顯示的時間為1分55秒<ref name="secretariat-BD"/><ref name="CNN@120621">{{Cite web |url = https://edition.cnn.com/2012/06/19/sport/secretariat-preakness-record/index.html |title = Secretariat's '73 Preakness time is a record, racing commission rules |author = CNN |date = 2012-06-21 |publisher = CNN |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-03 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180612150409/https://edition.cnn.com/2012/06/19/sport/secretariat-preakness-record/index.html |archivedate = 2018-06-12 }}</ref>。賓利高馬場的計時員其後宣佈秘書處的完成時間為1分54⅖秒，但《每日賽馬態況》的兩位計時員皆表示完成時間應該是1分53⅖秒，並將打破舊有的1分54秒紀錄<ref name="SI-WN@940919"/><ref name="DRF-MH@120619">{{Cite web |url = http://www.drf.com/news/secretariat-awarded-preakness-record-153-after-review |title = Secretariat awarded Preakness record at 1:53 after review |author = Matt Hegarty |date = 2012-06-19 |publisher = Daily Racing Form |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-03 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160324033138/http://www.drf.com/news/secretariat-awarded-preakness-record-153-after-review |archivedate = 2016-03-24 }}</ref>。其後，負責管理賓利高馬場的馬利蘭賽馬會宣佈不會參考電子計時器及《每日賽馬態況》所提出的完成時間，並視1分54⅖秒為官方時間紀錄<ref name="BH-SH@120620"/><ref name="DRF-MH@120619"/>。儘管馬利蘭賽馬會已公佈官方時間紀錄，《每日賽馬態況》的主編仍在報章內刊登自家計時員所錄得的1分53⅖秒時間紀錄<ref name="BH-SH@120620"/><ref name="DRF-MH@120619"/><ref name="Woolfe@p.192">Woolfe, p.192</ref>。

2012年6月19日，馬利蘭賽馬會應潘妮·切納里的要求，於{{tsl|en|Laurel Park (race track)|馬利蘭桂冠園}}舉行了一次特別會議，而她更聘請公司對比賽錄影帶進行審查<ref name="DRF-MH@120619"/>。聽證會持續兩至三小時，最終委員會一致同意將秘書處的時間紀錄由1分54⅖秒改為1分53秒，成為必利時錦標的新紀錄<ref name="CNN@120621">{{Cite web |url = https://edition.cnn.com/2012/06/19/sport/secretariat-preakness-record/index.html |title = Secretariat's '73 Preakness time is a record, racing commission rules |author = CNN |date = 2012-06-21 |publisher = CNN |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-03 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180612150409/https://edition.cnn.com/2012/06/19/sport/secretariat-preakness-record/index.html |archivedate = 2018-06-12 }}</ref>。《每日賽馬態況》其後宣佈會履行委員會有關於秘書處時間紀錄的裁決<ref name="DRF-MH@120619"/>。潘妮·切納里於會議後表示「在新的一天重新審視這場糾紛是解決問題的關鍵」，又指出「對歷史學家、體育記者及賽馬迷來說，他們的聲音得到了可靠證據的支持，而他們的聲音是值得被聆聽的」<ref name="CNN@120621"/>。

在秘書處為[[貝蒙錦標|貝蒙錦標]]作準備時，牠分別登上了《[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]》、《[[新聞週刊|新聞週刊]]》及《[[運動畫刊|運動畫刊]]》的封面，成為全國明星<ref name="NC-PK@150906"/><ref name="SI-WT@730618">{{Cite web |url = https://www.si.com/vault/1973/06/18/614651/history-in-the-making |title = History in the Making |author = Whitney Tower |date = 1973-06-18 |publisher = Sports Illustrated |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-03 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180212083523/https://www.si.com/vault/1973/06/18/614651/history-in-the-making |archivedate = 2018-02-12 }}</ref>。記者威廉·尼克（William Nack）更寫道：「秘書處突然超越了賽馬，成為了一種文化現象」<ref name="SI-WN@900604"/>。潘妮·切納里需要一名秘書處理所有的粉絲郵件，於是她聘請了{{tsl|en|William Morris Agency|威廉·莫里斯經紀公司}}負責管理<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.nytimes.com/1973/11/03/archives/secretariat-maybe-willbow-out-again-secretariat-maybe-one-more-race.html |title = Secretariat, Maybe, Will Bow Out Again |author = Steve Cady |date = 1973-11-03 |publisher = The New York Times |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-03 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180619100412/https://www.nytimes.com/1973/11/03/archives/secretariat-maybe-willbow-out-again-secretariat-maybe-one-more-race.html |archivedate = 2018-06-19 }}</ref>。另外，秘書處亦需要學懂在鏡頭前擺出姿勢<ref name="BH-SH@120604">{{Cite web |url = http://cs.bloodhorse.com/blogs/horse-racing-steve-haskin/archive/2012/06/04/haskin-s-belmont-report-remembering-big-red.aspx |title = Haskin's Belmont Report: Remembering Big Red |author = Steve Haskin |date = 2012-06-04 |publisher = Blood-Horse |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-03 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170917130101/http://cs.bloodhorse.com/blogs/horse-racing-steve-haskin/archive/2012/06/04/haskin-s-belmont-report-remembering-big-red.aspx |archivedate = 2017-09-17 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://articles.latimes.com/1989-10-05/sports/sp-994_1_horse-racing-notes |title = Secretariat Was Champion of the People, Both Young and Old |author = Bill Christine |date = 1989-10-05 |publisher = Los Angeles Times |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-03 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160819054403/http://articles.latimes.com/1989-10-05/sports/sp-994_1_horse-racing-notes |archivedate = 2016-08-19 }}</ref>。

==== 貝蒙錦標 ====
[[File:Secretariat_in_Belmont_Stakes.jpg|thumb]]
6月9日舉行的[[貝蒙錦標|貝蒙錦標]]只有五匹馬參賽，共有69,138人次入場觀看，是貝蒙錦標史上入場人數第二多的一屆<ref name="NYTimes-JN@730609">{{Cite web |url = https://archive.nytimes.com/www.nytimes.com/packages/html/sports/year_in_sports/06.09.html |title = A Horse for the Ages |author = Joe Nichols |date = 1973-06-09 |publisher = The New York Times |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-04 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180619100517/https://archive.nytimes.com/www.nytimes.com/packages/html/sports/year_in_sports/06.09.html |archivedate = 2018-06-19 }}</ref><ref name="AP@730610">{{Cite web |url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1356&dat=19730610&id=SAYkAAAAIBAJ&sjid=_AUEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6608,2219029 |title = Secretariat: A Triple Terror |author = Ocala Star-Banner |date = 1973-06-10 |publisher = Associated Press |language = EN |accessdate = 2018-06-04 |archive-date = 2022-01-19 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220119101910/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1356&dat=19730610&id=SAYkAAAAIBAJ&sjid=_AUEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6608%2C2219029 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。這場賽事由[[CBS_(電視網)|CBS]]轉播，超過1500多萬戶家庭觀看，佔其受眾份額52%<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.jockeyclub.com/roundtable/pdf/roundtable_73.pdf |title = Roundtable Discussion of the Jockey Club (1973) |author = Jockey Club |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-04 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160607190112/http://www.jockeyclub.com/roundtable/pdf/roundtable_73.pdf |archivedate = 2016-06-07 }}</ref>。賽事舉行當日的天氣溫暖且陽光明媚<ref name="AP@730610"/>。在比賽開始時，秘書處一反常態，牠在出閘後很快便領先，並用了23⅗秒跑畢首¼英里路程，第二段¼英里路程亦只是用了22⅗秒<ref name="AP@730610"/>。其後，秘書處繼續保持速度，開始與其他馬匹拉開距離，並以1分34⅕跑畢1英里路程<ref name="AP@730610"/>。儘管如此，秘書處並沒有減慢速度。騎師圖爾科特後來說：「這匹馬很聰明，我認為牠知道自己需要跑1½英里，我從未鞭策牠」<ref name="NYTimes-JN@730609"/>。最終，秘書處以31個馬位大勝對手，創下2分24秒的時間紀錄，並打破了1943年由另一匹馬所創下的25個馬位的紀錄<ref name="AP@730610"/><ref name="ESPN-RF">{{Cite web |url = http://www.espn.com/sportscentury/features/00016464.html |title = Secretariat remains No. 1 name in racing |author = Ron Flatter |publisher = ESPN.com |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-04 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170412025116/http://www.espn.com/sportscentury/features/00016464.html |archivedate = 2017-04-12 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://articles.latimes.com/1993-06-03/sports/sp-42813_1_belmont-park |title = Biggest Red : What Greater Run Than Secretariat's in the Belmont? |author = Bill Christine |date = 1993-06-03 |publisher = Los Angeles Times |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-04 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160601110000/http://articles.latimes.com/1993-06-03/sports/sp-42813_1_belmont-park |archivedate = 2016-06-01 }}</ref><ref name="壹蘋果馬網@070720">{{Cite web |url = http://hk.racing.nextmedia.com/art_main.php?sec_id=3400631&art_id=7343671&showdate=20070720 |title = 名駒錄：秘書處曾大勝31馬位 |author = 壹蘋果馬網 |date = 2007-07-20 |publisher = 蘋果日報有限公司 |language = zh-hk |accessdate = 2018-05-18 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180518200925/http://hk.racing.nextmedia.com/art_main.php?sec_id=3400631&art_id=7343671&showdate=20070720 |archivedate = 2018-05-18 }}</ref>。雜誌《{{tsl|en|The Blood-Horse|純血馬 (雜誌)|純血馬}}》的編輯肯特·霍林斯沃斯（Kent Hollingsworth）在秘書處接近終點時說：「我不相信。不可能。但我看到了。我無法呼吸。牠（秘書處）贏了，距離是十六份之一英里！我看到了。我必須相信」<ref name="BH-KH@730618">{{Cite web |url = https://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/187734/triple-crown-heroes-secretariat |title = Triple Crown Heroes: Secretariat |author = Kent Hollingsworth |date = 1973-06-18 |publisher = Blood-Horse |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-04 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180619100517/https://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/187734/triple-crown-heroes-secretariat |archivedate = 2018-06-19 }}</ref>。另外，CBS的主持切奇·安德森（Chic Anderson）曾經在一篇著名的評論中描述了秘書處的速度：
{{quote|「秘書處與其他馬匹的距離愈來愈遠！牠移動時好像一部巨大的機器！」<ref name="ESPN-RF"/><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.vancouversun.com/sports/This+history+June+1973/6764080/story.html |title = This day in history: June 9, 1973 |author = Vancouver Sun |date = 2012-11-06 |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-04 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161009085219/http://www.vancouversun.com/sports/This+history+June+1973/6764080/story.html |archivedate = 2016-10-09 }}</ref>}}

秘書處的完成時間，2分24秒，不僅打破了貝蒙錦標的最快紀錄，更創下了歷史上1½英里泥地的最快紀錄<ref name="ESPN-RF"/>。秘書處在1½英里泥地所創下的紀錄至今仍然未被打破<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.equibase.com/about/northamericanrecords.cfm |title = North American Records - Dirt Course |author = Equibase |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-04 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180423093044/http://www.equibase.com/about/northamericanrecords.cfm |archivedate = 2018-04-23 }}</ref>。如果在那時候{{tsl|en|Beyer Speed Figure|貝葉爾速度圖}}已經存在的話，安德魯·貝葉爾（Andrew Beyer）計算出秘書處的數字為139，是他有史以來得出的最高數字<ref name="WP-AB@101007"/><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.drf.com/products/beyers/beyers.html |title = Daily Racing Form: Beyer Numbers |author = Daily Racing Form |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-04 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160707190245/http://www1.drf.com/products/beyers/beyers.html |archivedate = 2016-07-07}}</ref>。

在賽事開始前數小時，人群便開始聚集於{{tsl|en|Belmont Park|貝蒙園}}附近，很多早前錯過比賽的人都希望能近距離看到馬匹<ref name="BH-KH@730618"/>。秘書處及潘妮·切納里受到熱烈歡迎，而切納里則以揮手及微笑作回應<ref name="BH-KH@730618"/>。在賽事開始前秘書處出場會伴隨著很大的歡呼聲，但隨著比賽開始，人們兩個最常見的反應是對秘書處速度過快的懷疑和擔憂<ref name="SI-WN@900604"/><ref name="SI-WT@730618"/><ref name="BH-KH@730618"/><ref>Woolfe, pp. 121–122</ref>。當秘書處顯然獲得勝利時，據說人群的聲音會令看台出現震動的情況<ref name="BH-SH@120604"/>。

這場賽事廣泛地被認為是二十世紀北美賽馬史上其中一場最精彩的比賽<ref name="SI-WT@730618"/><ref name="Atlantic-AC@130607">{{Cite web |url = https://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2013/06/secretariats-jockey-on-winning-the-triple-crown-at-belmont-40-years-ago/276453/ |title = Secretariat's Jockey on Winning the Triple Crown at Belmont, 40 Years Ago |author = Andrew Cohen |date = 2013-06-07 |publisher = The Atlantic |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-04 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180212083508/https://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2013/06/secretariats-jockey-on-winning-the-triple-crown-at-belmont-40-years-ago/276453/ |archivedate = 2018-02-12 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.latimes.com/sports/sportsnow/la-sp-sn-ranking-the-triple-crown-winners-20150605-story.html |title = Ranking the Triple Crown winners |author = John Cherwa |date = 2015-06-05 |publisher = Los Angeles Times |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-04 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180619100517/http://www.latimes.com/sports/sportsnow/la-sp-sn-ranking-the-triple-crown-winners-20150605-story.html |archivedate = 2018-06-19 }}</ref>。秘書處成為歷史上第九位美國三冠大賽的冠軍，是相隔25年來再有馬匹成為大賽冠軍<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/triple-crown/triple-crown-winners |title = Triple Crown Winners |author = Blood-Horse |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-04 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180203075403/https://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/triple-crown/triple-crown-winners |archivedate = 2018-02-03 }}</ref>。在賽事結束後，大約有5,427張投注秘書處[[獨贏|獨贏]]的彩票未被兌現，有報章推測這群投注者可能視這些彩票為紀念品，因為2美元的彩票派彩僅為2.20美元<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=2519&dat=19730711&id=YORdAAAAIBAJ&sjid=BV8NAAAAIBAJ&pg=1480,1457892&hl=en |title = Souvenir hunters failing to cash in on triple crown winner |author = Observer-Reporter |date = 1973-07-11 |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-04 |archive-date = 2022-01-19 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220119101919/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=2519&dat=19730711&id=YORdAAAAIBAJ&sjid=BV8NAAAAIBAJ&pg=1480%2C1457892&hl=en |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

==== 阿靈頓邀請賽 ====
在秘書處勝出貝蒙錦標後三週，牠被運至{{tsl|en|Arlington Park|阿靈頓公園}}參加{{tsl|en|Secretariat Stakes|阿靈頓邀請賽}}。勞林在接受雜誌《純血馬》訪問時說：「如果你還記得的話，在貝蒙錦標之前我也說過這番話，我真的不知道如何讓這匹馬休息。牠（秘書處）非常強壯，而且精力充沛。雖然現時只是貝蒙錦標過後的一星期多，但請相信我，如果我不準許這匹馬參賽的話，牠可能會在馬廄內自殘。所以我們決定安排牠在芝加哥參賽，讓[[美國中西部|中西部]]的人有機會看到牠」<ref name="BH-FA@150623">{{Cite web |url = https://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/106709/first-start-back-after-a-triple-crown |title = First Start Back After a Triple Crown |author = Frank Angst |date = 2015-06-23 |publisher = Blood-Horse |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-05 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170710085647/http://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/106709/first-start-back-after-a-triple-crown |archivedate = 2017-07-10 }}</ref>。阿靈頓邀請賽的賽程是1⅛英里，而獎金是125,000美元<ref name="BH-FA@150623"/>。芝加哥市長[[李察·米高·戴利|理查德·M·達利]]甚至宣佈賽事舉行的星期六是「秘書處日」（Secretariat Day）<ref>Capps, p. 168</ref>。

6月30日，阿靈頓邀請賽舉行當日，共有41,223人次入場觀看<ref name="Gitlin">Gitlin, p. 163-164</ref>。在賽事中，秘書處雖然起步較慢，但之後牠很快便領先，最終以9個馬位勝出，時間為1分47秒<ref name="Gitlin"/><ref name="SI-GP@730709">{{Cite web |url = https://www.si.com/vault/1973/07/09/606526/crunch-went-the-big-red-apple |title = Crunch went the Big Red Apple |author = George Plimpton |date = 1973-07-09 |publisher = Sports Illustrated |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-05 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161010001926/http://www.si.com/vault/1973/07/09/606526/crunch-went-the-big-red-apple |archivedate = 2016-10-10 }}</ref>。記者喬治·普林普頓（George Plimpton）在其報導內說：「秘書處的事跡可能會流傳一個世紀」<ref name="SI-GP@730709"/>。

==== 惠特尼錦標 ====
在三冠大賽過後，秘書處回到{{tsl|en|Saratoga Race Course|沙拉托加馬場}}，準備在8月4日舉行的{{tsl|en|Whitney Handicap|惠特尼錦標}}<ref name="Guardian-TG@150801">{{Cite web |url = https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2015/aug/01/forgotten-story-onion-secretariat-triple-crown |title = The forgotten story of Onion, the horse who beat the 1973 Triple Crown winner |author = Teresa Genaro |date = 2015-08-01 |publisher = The Guardian |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-06 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180609075749/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2015/aug/01/forgotten-story-onion-secretariat-triple-crown |archivedate = 2018-06-09 }}</ref>。7月27日，秘書處在訓練時分別以1分34秒跑畢1英里及以1分47⅘秒跑畢1⅛英里，非正式地打破了賽馬場的紀錄<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.nytimes.com/1973/07/28/archives/sarotoga-gets-sample-of-secretariats-speed.html |title = Saratoga Gets Sample Of Secretariat's Speed |author = The New York Times |date = 1973-07-28 |publisher = The New York Times |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-06 |archive-date = 2018-06-12 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180612194749/https://www.nytimes.com/1973/07/28/archives/sarotoga-gets-sample-of-secretariats-speed.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。賽事舉行當日，賽道的狀況被評為快地，但馬匹在賽道上跑得較慢，特別是內欄位置<ref name="NYTimes-JN@730805"/>。在賽事中，秘書處起步較慢，而另一匹四歲馬很快便領先，其後騎師圖爾科特發現秘書處的反應比平時緩慢，他便開始揮鞭，最終以1個馬位之差獲得賽事亞軍<ref name="NYTimes-JN@730805">{{Cite web |url = https://www.nytimes.com/1973/08/05/archives/onion-upsets-110-secretariat-winning-whitney-by-a-length.html |title = Onion Upsets 1‐10 Secretariat, Winning Whitney by a Length |author = Joe Nichols |date = 1973-08-05 |publisher = The New York Times |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-06 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180619100409/https://www.nytimes.com/1973/08/05/archives/onion-upsets-110-secretariat-winning-whitney-by-a-length.html |archivedate = 2018-06-19 }}</ref>。有報章更記錄到有超過30,000人在秘書處落敗後露出苦惱的情緒<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=6mseAAAAIBAJ&sjid=dckEAAAAIBAJ&pg=872,1115749&dq=secretariat+onion&hl=en |title = Secretariat beaten! |author = Daytona Beach Morning Journal |date = 1973-08-05 |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-06 |archive-date = 2020-04-20 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200420230008/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=6mseAAAAIBAJ&sjid=dckEAAAAIBAJ&pg=872%2C1115749&dq=secretariat+onion&hl=en |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

儘管冠軍馬匹的練馬師{{tsl|en|H. Allen Jerkens|艾倫·傑爾金斯}}人稱「巨人殺手」<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.nytimes.com/2015/03/19/sports/allen-jerkens-giant-killer-of-horse-racing-dies-at-85.html |title = Allen Jerkens, ‘Giant Killer’ of Horse Racing, Dies at 85 |author = Richard Goldstein |date = 2015-03-19 |publisher = The New York Times |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-06 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151017040920/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/03/19/sports/allen-jerkens-giant-killer-of-horse-racing-dies-at-85.html |archivedate = 2015-10-17 }}</ref>，但秘書處的落敗可能是由病毒感染引起，並導致牠出現低燒和腹瀉症狀<ref name="DRF-JH@130802">{{Cite web |url = http://www.drf.com/news/jay-hovdey-day-onion-slayed-secretariat |title = Jay Hovdey: The day Onion slayed Secretariat |author = Jay Hovdey |date = 2013-08-02 |publisher = Daily Racing Form |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-06 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170901014426/http://www.drf.com/news/jay-hovdey-day-onion-slayed-secretariat |archivedate = 2017-09-01 }}</ref>。潘妮·切納里在賽後表示：「在賽馬場上什麼事情都可能會發生，當時的我正在學習這一點。我們知道牠（秘書處）受感染的機率很低，但是我們認為牠夠強大，足以勝出比賽，顯然是我們錯了」<ref name="DRF-JH@130802"/>。秘書處在生病後失去了食慾，而且持續數天都是行動遲緩<ref name="BH-SH@080804">{{Cite web |url = http://cs.bloodhorse.com/blogs/horse-racing-steve-haskin/archive/2008/08/04/The-Unbeatable-Horse.aspx |title = The Unbeatable Horse |author = Steve Haskin |date = 2008-08-04 |publisher = Blood-Horse |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-06 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160808160201/http://cs.bloodhorse.com/blogs/horse-racing-steve-haskin/archive/2008/08/04/The-Unbeatable-Horse.aspx |archivedate = 2016-08-08 }}</ref>。資深體育記者查爾斯·哈頓（Charles Hatton）在報導內寫道：「秘書處走路時看來很痛苦，而且牠無緣參加{{tsl|en|Travers Stakes|特拉弗斯錦標}}。牠需要不可思議的恢復能力才能恢復過來。牠在兩星期內接受了四次嚴格的訓練，而令人驚訝的是，牠在每次練習都有收獲，而體重亦有增加」<ref name="DRF-DI@100923"/>。

==== 萬寶路杯 ====
9月12日，秘書處為{{tsl|en|Marlboro Cup Invitational Handicap|萬寶路杯}}進行最後一次訓練，先以57秒跑畢5[[化朗|化朗]]，然後更以1分8⅘秒完成額外的1化朗（共6化朗）路程<ref>Capps, p. 176</ref>。9月15日，秘書處回到貝蒙園並參加首屆萬寶路杯，而這次賽事共有48,023人次入場觀看<ref name="TSU">{{cite news |author = The Springfield union, Massachusetts |title = Big Red Sets World Record - Secretariat Delivers |publisher = The Springfield union, Massachusetts |pages = p. 1 |date = 1973-09-15 |accessdate = 2018-06-06 |language = en}}</ref><ref name="NYTimes-JN@730916">{{Cite web |url = https://www.nytimes.com/1973/09/16/archives/secretariat-wins-setting-a-world-record-margin-312-lengths.html |title = Secretariat Wins, Setting a World Record |author = Joe Nichols |date = 1973-09-16 |publisher = The New York Times |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-06 |archive-date = 2018-06-12 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180612213352/https://www.nytimes.com/1973/09/16/archives/secretariat-wins-setting-a-world-record-margin-312-lengths.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。雖然在賽事舉行的前一晚曾經下雨，但在正午時份賽道已經乾透<ref>Capps, p. 177</ref>。在比賽中，秘書處在起跑很快便居於第五位，以22⅗秒完成首¼英里，其後牠趁其他馬匹速度回落之際開始追上，最終以1分45⅖完成1⅛英里路程，拋離對手3½個馬位勝出賽事<ref name="NYTimes-JN@730916"/><ref>Capps, pp. 178-179</ref><ref>Scanlan, p. 166</ref>。另外，秘書處在1⅛英里泥地路程所創下的時間紀錄更成為了世界紀錄<ref name="NYTimes-JN@730916"/><ref name="Duke@p.16">Duke, p. 16</ref>。賽後，騎師圖爾科特表示：「今日牠已經成長為老秘書處，而且牠依靠自己便做到了」<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.si.com/vault/1973/09/24/618055/they-made-pigeons-of-the-field |title = They made pigeons of the field |author = Whitney Tower |date = 1973-09-24 |publisher = Sports Illustrated |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-06 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161009182347/http://www.si.com/vault/1973/09/24/618055/they-made-pigeons-of-the-field |archivedate = 2016-10-09 }}</ref>。萬寶路杯的獎金為25萬美元，而獲勝的秘書處則在這場比賽後成為有史以來第十三匹奪得超過一百萬元獎金的純種馬<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://cs.bloodhorse.com/blogs/racinghub/archive/2013/09/23/marlboro-cup-of-champions.aspx |title = Marlboro Cup of Champions |author = Mike Sekulic |date = 2013-09-23 |publisher = Blood-Horse |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-06 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170817123443/http://cs.bloodhorse.com/blogs/racinghub/archive/2013/09/23/marlboro-cup-of-champions.aspx |archivedate = 2017-08-17 }}</ref>。

==== 伍德沃德錦標 ====
在萬寶路杯後，原定的計劃是由馬廄的另一匹競賽馬參加於9月30日舉行的{{tsl|en|Woodward Stakes|伍德沃德錦標}}，而秘書處則為10月舉行的{{tsl|en|Man o' War Stakes|鬥士錦標}}作準備<ref name="NYTimes-SC@731002">{{Cite web |url = https://www.nytimes.com/1973/10/02/archives/secretariat-riva-ridge-to-race-monday-at-atlantic-city.html |title = Secretariat, Riva Ridge to Race Monday |author = Steve Cady |date = 1973-10-02 |publisher = The New York Times |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-07 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180201110230/http://www.nytimes.com/1973/10/02/archives/secretariat-riva-ridge-to-race-monday-at-atlantic-city.html |archivedate = 2018-02-01 }}</ref><ref name="Scanlan@p.167">Scanlan, p. 167</ref>。但由於賽事舉行前曾經下雨，賽道較濕，而該匹競賽馬不善於應付這類型的賽道，因此改由秘書處參賽<ref name="Duke@p.16"/><ref name="NYTimes-SC@731002"/>。這次賽事共有32,117人次入場觀看<ref name="NYTimes-JN@730930">{{Cite web |url = https://www.nytimes.com/1973/09/30/archives/161-prove-out-wins-secretariat-is-2d-secretariat-beaten-by-a-161.html |title = 16‐1 Prove Out Wins |author = Joe Nichols |date = 1973-09-30 |publisher = The New York Times |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-07 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180612173918/https://www.nytimes.com/1973/09/30/archives/161-prove-out-wins-secretariat-is-2d-secretariat-beaten-by-a-161.html |archivedate = 2018-06-12 }}</ref>。在比賽開始後，秘書處雖然很快取得領先位置，並與第二位有著1個馬位的距離，但牠其後被另一匹四歲的競賽馬超前，最終以4½個馬位之差成為賽事亞軍<ref name="Duke@p.16"/><ref name="NYTimes-JN@730930"/><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=mKkbAAAAIBAJ&sjid=hVQEAAAAIBAJ&pg=7403,6275655&dq=secretariat+prove-out&hl=en |title = Prove Out beats Secretariat |author = Pittsburgh Press |date = 1973-09-30 |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-07 |archive-date = 2020-04-20 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200420230109/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=mKkbAAAAIBAJ&sjid=hVQEAAAAIBAJ&pg=7403%2C6275655&dq=secretariat+prove-out&hl=en |dead-url = no }}</ref>。賽後，騎師圖爾科特對秘書處的失敗感到困惑，指出牠在領先時的表現很不錯，「我只是不知道牠發生了什麼事，也許牠未能掌握這條賽道」<ref name="NYTimes-JN@730930"/>。

==== 鬥士錦標 ====
10月8日，僅是伍德沃德錦標舉行後的9天，秘書處參加在貝蒙園舉行的{{tsl|en|Man o' War Stakes|鬥士錦標}}，而這次更是牠首次在草地賽道上作賽<ref name="Nelson@p.1178">Nelson, p. 1178</ref>。在這場賽事中共有七匹競賽馬參賽，其中包括一匹曾經於1⅛英里草地賽道上創下世界紀錄的競賽馬<ref name="NYRA-BE@170512">{{Cite web |url = https://www.nyra.com/belmont/news/man-o%E2%80%99war-stakes-win-proved-secretariat%E2%80%99s-supremacy-on-turf |title = Man o’War Stakes win proved Secretariat’s supremacy on turf |author = Bob Ehalt |date = 2017-05-12 |publisher = The New York Racing Association |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-07 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180612140831/https://www.nyra.com/belmont/news/man-o%E2%80%99war-stakes-win-proved-secretariat%E2%80%99s-supremacy-on-turf |archivedate = 2018-06-12 }}</ref>。在比賽中，秘書處在起步後很快便領先，而第二位的馬匹亦開始收窄差距，但當秘書處跑至第八段柱時牠已經拋離對手3個馬位，最終以2分24⅘秒完成1½英里路程，拋離對手5個馬位勝出賽事<ref name="Scanlan@p.167"/><ref name="Nelson@p.1178"/><ref name="NYRA-BE@170512"/><ref>Capps, p. 184</ref>。2017年，秘書處的騎師圖爾科特於家中接受訪問時說：「人們不會相信我，但是秘書處在草地上的表現的確比在泥地上出色。牠在草地上的移動方式就好像是另一匹馬。一旦踏上草地，牠就好像突然間成熟起來」<ref name="NYRA-BE@170512"/>。

==== 加拿大國際錦標 ====
基於1973年初出售秘書處時所訂下的協議，秘書處需要在1973年底退役，因此10月28日於[[加拿大|加拿大]][[多倫多|多倫多]]{{tsl|en|Woodbine Racetrack|活拜馬場}}舉行的{{tsl|en|Canadian International Stakes|加拿大國際錦標}}是秘書處的競賽生涯中最後一場比賽<ref name="ESPN-RF"/><ref name="TS-DP@101015">{{Cite web |url = https://www.thestar.com/sports/2010/10/15/perkins_secretariat_one_of_a_kind.html |title = Secretariat one of a kind |author = Dave Perkins |date = 2010-10-15 |publisher = Toronto Star |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-09 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170826031439/https://www.thestar.com/sports/2010/10/15/perkins_secretariat_one_of_a_kind.html |archivedate = 2017-08-26 }}</ref>。選擇這場賽事的原因是因為切納里家族與加拿大實業家{{tsl|en|E. P. Taylor|E·P·泰勒}}有著密切的關係<ref name="CHRHF">{{Cite web |url = http://www.canadianhorseracinghalloffame.com/2013/08/17/secretariat/ |title = Secretariat – Canadian Horse Racing Hall of Fame |author = Canadian Horse Racing Hall of Fame |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-09 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180619100415/http://www.canadianhorseracinghalloffame.com/2013/08/17/secretariat/ |archivedate = 2018-06-19 }}</ref><ref name="TRC-ES@171009">{{Cite web |url = https://www.thoroughbredracing.com/articles/how-secretariat-gave-canadians-something-remember-ever/ |title = How Secretariat gave the Canadians something to remember for ever |author = Emily Shields |date = 2017-10-09 |publisher = Thoroughbred Racing Commentary |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-09 |archive-date = 2019-09-20 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190920192108/https://www.thoroughbredracing.com/articles/how-secretariat-gave-canadians-something-remember-ever/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>，而且秘書處的練馬師勞林及騎師圖爾科特皆是加拿大人<ref name="TS-DP@101015"/><ref name="TRC-ES@171009"/>。可惜的是，圖爾科特因被停賽5天而無緣參加這項賽事，因此秘書處改由{{tsl|en|Eddie Maple|埃迪·馬普爾}}策騎<ref name="NYTimes-MS@731026">{{Cite web |url = https://www.nytimes.com/1973/10/26/archives/turcotte-suspended-5-days-maple-will-ride-secretariat-ronturcotte.html |title = Turcotte Suspended 5 Days; Maple Will Ride Secretariat |author = Michael Strauss |date = 1973-10-26 |publisher = The New York Times |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-09 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180612205104/https://www.nytimes.com/1973/10/26/archives/turcotte-suspended-5-days-maple-will-ride-secretariat-ronturcotte.html |archivedate = 2018-06-12 }}</ref>。

賽事舉行當日的天氣寒冷，多風而且潮濕，但草地賽道的狀況並未出現問題<ref name="TRC-ES@171010">{{Cite web |url = https://www.thoroughbredracing.com/articles/day-drama-secretariat-delivers-ultimate-sign-/ |title = A day of drama as Secretariat delivers the ultimate sign-off |author = Emily Shields |date = 2017-10-10 |publisher = Thoroughbred Racing Commentary |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-09 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180612142733/https://www.thoroughbredracing.com/articles/day-drama-secretariat-delivers-ultimate-sign-/ |archivedate = 2018-06-12 }}</ref>。儘管天氣如此，這埸賽事仍有約35,000人入場觀看<ref name="TRC-ES@171010"/>。在比賽開始後，其中一匹競賽馬Kennedy Road隨即狂奔並處於領先位置，秘書處則在離開外疊後位居第二，而當秘書處與Kennedy Road平排時，Kennedy Road更數次撞擊秘書處<ref name="TRC-ES@171010"/>。其後，秘書處超越Kennedy Road並處於領先位置，且開始拋離其他馬匹，最終秘書處以2分41⅘秒完成1⅝英里路程，在拋離對手6½個馬位的情況下勝出賽事<ref name="TS-DP@101015"/><ref name="TRC-ES@171010"/>。在賽後出現了如貝蒙錦標一樣的情況，有為數不少的投注秘書處的彩票未被兌現<ref name="TS-DP@101015"/>。

=== 退役 ===
11月6日，賽事結束後9天，秘書處被帶至雅佳特馬場，與騎師圖爾科特作最後一次的公開露面，而當時大約有32,900人出席<ref name="ESPN-LS@031119">{{Cite web |url = https://www.espn.com/classic/s/secretariatadd.html |title = Secretariat demolished Belmont field |author = Larry Schwartz |date = 2003-11-19 |publisher = ESPN.com |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-09 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180612141456/https://www.espn.com/classic/s/secretariatadd.html |archivedate = 2018-06-12 }}</ref><ref name="NYTimes-MS@731030">{{Cite web |url = https://www.nytimes.com/1973/10/30/archives/secretariat-will-parade-at-aqueduct-secretariat-will-parade-at.html |title = Secretariat Will Parade At Aqueduct |author = Michael Strauss |date = 1973-10-30 |publisher = The New York Times |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-09 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180619100409/https://www.nytimes.com/1973/10/30/archives/secretariat-will-parade-at-aqueduct-secretariat-will-parade-at.html |archivedate = 2018-06-19 }}</ref>。練馬師勞林在接受訪問時表示：「這是一個悲傷的日子，也是美好的一日。我當然希望牠（秘書處）在四歲時仍能奔跑，牠是一匹很棒的馬，牠喜歡奔跑」<ref name="NYTimes-JN@731107">{{Cite web |url = https://www.nytimes.com/1973/11/07/archives/a-ceremonial-windup-for-secretariat-super-red-parades-in-silks-to.html |title = A Ceremonial Windup for Secretariat |author = Joe Nichols |date = 1973-11-07 |publisher = The New York Times |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-09 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180619100409/https://www.nytimes.com/1973/11/07/archives/a-ceremonial-windup-for-secretariat-super-red-parades-in-silks-to.html |archivedate = 2018-06-19 }}</ref>。

在1973年尾，秘書處再度獲評為年度馬王，並奪得{{tsl|en|American Champion Three-Year-Old Male Horse|美國最佳三歲雄馬}}及{{tsl|en|American Champion Male Turf Horse|美國最佳草地馬}}獎項<ref name="AP-MG@731219">{{Cite web |url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=hhMyAAAAIBAJ&sjid=6aEFAAAAIBAJ&pg=2262,698356&dq=secretariat+horse-of-the-year&hl=en |title = Triple Crown winner Secretariat sweeps Horse of the Year ballotting |author = Montreal Gazette |date = 1973-12-19 |publisher = Associated Press |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-09 |archive-date = 2020-04-20 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200420230138/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=hhMyAAAAIBAJ&sjid=6aEFAAAAIBAJ&pg=2262%2C698356&dq=secretariat+horse-of-the-year&hl=en |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== 競賽成績 ===
在秘書處的競賽生涯中，牠先後參與了21場賽事，當中勝出16次、獲得3次亞軍及1次季軍，共贏得1,316,808美元獎金<ref name="Profile of Secretariat"/>。秘書處亦先後獲得5項日蝕獎，包括美國年度馬王、美國最佳兩歲雄馬、美國最佳三歲雄馬以及美國最佳草地馬<ref name="Bowen@p.17-18"/><ref name="AP-MG@731219"/>。
