== 配種生涯 ==
秘書處在退役後被運至克萊伯恩農場，開始牠的配種生涯。然而，秘書處的精子出現了未成熟的跡象<ref name="DRF-DI@100923"/>，因此牠需要在1973年12月與三匹非純種馬進行配種，以測試生育能力<ref name="NYTimes@740104">{{Cite web |url = https://www.nytimes.com/1974/01/04/archives/secretariat-declared-fertile-test-mare-in-foal.html |title = Secretariat Declared Fertile |author = The New York Times |date = 1974-01-04 |publisher = The New York Times |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-11 |archive-date = 2018-06-12 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180612152418/https://www.nytimes.com/1974/01/04/archives/secretariat-declared-fertile-test-mare-in-foal.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。一旦秘書處無法生育，牠將會返回原本所屬的馬廄並重新開始競賽，投資者將會取回他們投入的資金，而潘妮·切納里則可以於保險公司手上取得608萬美元<ref name="NYTimes-TB@730923">{{Cite web |url = https://www.nytimes.com/1973/09/23/archives/when-secretariat-stands-at-stud-all-you-can-do-is-breed-the-best.html |title = All you can do is breed the best with the best |author = Tom Buckley |date = 1973-09-23 |publisher = The New York Times |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-11 |archive-date = 2018-06-12 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180612220144/https://www.nytimes.com/1973/09/23/archives/when-secretariat-stands-at-stud-all-you-can-do-is-breed-the-best.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。1974年1月3日，克萊伯恩農場的經理H·K·泰勒（H. K. Taylor）宣佈秘書處具備生育能力，而其中一匹名為Leola的{{tsl|en|Appaloosa|阿帕盧薩馬}}亦已懷孕<ref name="NYTimes@740104"/><ref name="Hunter@p.435-436">Hunter, pp. 435-436</ref>。同年11月，Leola誕下秘書處的首匹子嗣<ref name="Hunter@p.435-436"/>。這匹馬駒被命名為First Secretary，毛色與秘書處同樣是栗色，但身上的班點則像秘書處的母系<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.drf.com/blogs/top-beyers-secretariats-first-foal-arlington-pars |title = Top Beyers, Secretariat's First Foal, Arlington Pars |author = Dan Illman |date = 2011-02-07 |publisher = Daily Racing Form |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-11 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180612142742/http://www.drf.com/blogs/top-beyers-secretariats-first-foal-arlington-pars |archivedate = 2018-06-12 }}</ref>。

秘書處首批純種子嗣於1975年出生，共28匹<ref name="SP@120425">{{Cite web |url = https://www.sportingpost.co.za/2012/04/secretariat-great-sire-or-a-dud-at-stud/ |title = Secretariat – great sire or a dud at stud? |author = Sporting Post |date = 2012-04-25 |publisher = Sporting Post |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-12 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161009184805/http://www.sportingpost.co.za/2012/04/secretariat-great-sire-or-a-dud-at-stud/ |archivedate = 2016-10-09 }}</ref>。在這批子嗣內，成績最好的是曾於1977年10月勝出{{tsl|en|Racing Post Trophy|威廉希爾未來錦標}}的Dactylographer<ref name="SP@120425"/>。此外，同屬這批子嗣的Canadian Bound在1976年的{{tsl|en|Keeneland Sales|基恩蘭拍賣會}}上以150萬美元售出，同時是首次有一歲馬的售價突破100萬美元關口<ref name="Cassidy">Cassidy, p. xxiv</ref>。然而，Canadian Bound在競賽方面完全失敗，牠先後四次參加賽事但均未能取得勝利<ref name="Cassidy"/><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/164340/a-memorable-date-first-seven-figure-yearling-sold |title = A Memorable Date: First Seven-Figure Yearling Sold |author = Blood-Horse |date = 2006-07-20 |publisher = Blood-Horse |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-12 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170823101608/https://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/164340/a-memorable-date-first-seven-figure-yearling-sold |archivedate = 2017-08-23 }}</ref>。更甚的是，歷經多年秘書處後代的價值大幅下降，反觀[[北地舞人|北地舞人]]的後代則在拍賣會上變得普及<ref name="BH-DS@010715">{{Cite web |url = https://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/192443/era-ends-with-mr-prospectors-last-foal-crop |title = Era Ends With Mr. Prospector's Last Foal Crop |author = David Schmitz |date = 2001-07-15 |publisher = Blood-Horse |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-12 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170430074854/http://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/192443/era-ends-with-mr-prospectors-last-foal-crop |archivedate = 2017-04-30 }}</ref>。

