* General Assembly：1979年{{tsl|en|Travers Stakes|特拉弗斯錦標}}的勝出者，其創下的2分鐘賽道紀錄維持了37年<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/sports/1979/08/19/general-assembly-shows-his-heels/6753e155-5e85-468f-8574-8d2f3f35c2cf/?noredirect=on&utm_term=.37b6293418c3 |title = General Assembly Shows His Heels |author = Andrew Beyer |date = 1979-08-19 |publisher = Washington Post |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-12 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180612145319/https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/sports/1979/08/19/general-assembly-shows-his-heels/6753e155-5e85-468f-8574-8d2f3f35c2cf/?noredirect=on&utm_term=.37b6293418c3 |archivedate = 2018-06-12 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/214597/baffert-reflects-on-arrogates-travers-romp |title = Baffert Reflects on Arrogate's Travers Romp |author = Blood-Horse |date = 2016-08-28 |publisher = Blood-Horse |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-12 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170726152707/http://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/214597/baffert-reflects-on-arrogates-travers-romp |archivedate = 2017-07-26 }}</ref>。
* Lady's Secret：1985年{{tsl|en|Ballerina Stakes|芭樂蓮娜錦標}}的勝出者，1986年年度馬王<ref name="TS-TP@160725">{{Cite web |url = https://www.americasbestracing.net/the-sport/2016-ladys-secret-horse-racings-iron-lady |title = Lady’s Secret: Horse Racing’s Iron Lady |author = Tom Pedulla |date = 2016-07-25 |publisher = The Sport |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-12 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170323040521/https://www.americasbestracing.net/the-sport/2016-ladys-secret-horse-racings-iron-lady |archivedate = 2017-03-23 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.drf.com/news/ladys-secret-dead-age-21 |title = Lady's Secret dead at age 21 |author = Glenye Cain Oakford |date = 2003-03-04 |publisher = Daily Racing Form |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-12 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20171108225931/http://www.drf.com/news/ladys-secret-dead-age-21 |archivedate = 2017-11-08 }}</ref>。
* Risen Star：1988年{{tsl|en|Louisiana Derby|路易斯安那打吡}}、[[必利時錦標|必利時錦標]]及[[貝蒙錦標|貝蒙錦標]]的勝出者<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/226596/louisiana-derby-led-risen-star-to-the-classics |title = Louisiana Derby Led Risen Star to the Classics |author = Tom Hall |date = 2018-03-21 |publisher = Blood-Horse |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-12 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180612162138/https://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/226596/louisiana-derby-led-risen-star-to-the-classics |archivedate = 2018-06-12 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.nytimes.com/1988/06/12/sports/risen-star-runs-away-with-the-belmont.html |title = Risen Star Runs Away With the Belmont |author = Steven Crist |date = 1988-06-12 |publisher = The New York Times |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-12 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180612200224/https://www.nytimes.com/1988/06/12/sports/risen-star-runs-away-with-the-belmont.html |archivedate = 2018-06-12 }}</ref>。
* {{tsl|en|Kingston Rule|京士頓令}}：1990年{{tsl|en|Marlboro Cup Invitational Handicap|萬寶路杯}}勝出者，更打破場地紀錄<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/132791/melbourne-cup-winner-kingston-rule-dies |title = Melbourne Cup Winner Kingston Rule Dies |author = Blood-Horse |date = 2011-12-08 |publisher = Blood-Horse |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-12 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170427100830/http://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/132791/melbourne-cup-winner-kingston-rule-dies |archivedate = 2017-04-27 }}</ref>。
