* Betty's Secret：1984年[[葉森打吡大賽|葉森打吡大賽]]的優勝者{{link-en|Secreto}}及1998年至2000年{{tsl|en|Champion Hurdle|冠軍跳欄賽}}的優勝者{{link-en|Istabraq}}的母系<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.thoroughbreddailynews.com/pdf/opp/opp030227.pdf |title = The Royal Ascot of Jumping |author = Bill Oppenheim |date = 2003-02-27 |publisher = Thoroughbred Daily News |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-13 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161009182900/http://www.thoroughbreddailynews.com/pdf/opp/opp030227.pdf |archivedate = 2016-10-09 }}</ref>。

透過{{link-en|Weekend Surprise}}及{{link-en|Terlingua|Terlingua (horse)}}，秘書處的血脈得以出現於眾多冠軍馬匹的譜系內。Weekend Surprise的兒子{{link-en|A.P. Indy}}在2003年及2006年曾獲評為{{tsl|en|Leading sire in North America|北美著名父系馬}}<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.americasbestracing.net/the-sport/2017-ap-indy-destined-greatness |title = A.P. Indy: Destined for Greatness |author = Tom Pedulla |date = 2017-12-11 |publisher = The Sport |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-14 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20171223085923/https://www.americasbestracing.net/the-sport/2017-ap-indy-destined-greatness |archivedate = 2017-12-23 }}</ref>，而牠更是2003年年度馬王{{link-en|Mineshaft|Mineshaft (horse)}}及2007年貝蒙錦標優勝者{{tsl|en|Rags to Riches (horse)|青雲路 (馬)|青雲路}}的父系<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.kentucky.com/sports/horses/article44088864.html |title = Leading sire A.P. Indy retired from breeding |author = Alicia Wincze Hughes |date = 2011-04-09 |publisher = Lexington Herald Leader |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-14 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170510095526/http://www.kentucky.com/sports/horses/article44088864.html |archivedate = 2017-05-10 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.cbsnews.com/news/rags-to-riches-wins-the-belmont/ |title = Rags To Riches Wins The Belmont |author = James Klatell |date = 2007-06-09 |publisher = CBS |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-14 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180614171620/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/rags-to-riches-wins-the-belmont/ |archivedate = 2018-06-14 }}</ref>。A.P. Indy的種馬後裔亦繁殖了不少的優秀馬匹，例如被評為2014年至2016年北美著名父系馬的Tapit<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.cnbc.com/2018/05/03/forget-the-races-the-real-money-is-made-in-stud-fees.html |title = Forget the Belmont Stakes, the real money is made from being a stud |author = Christina Medici Scolaro |date = 2018-05-04 |publisher = CNBC |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-14 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180504095148/https://www.cnbc.com/2018/05/03/forget-the-races-the-real-money-is-made-in-stud-fees.html |archivedate = 2018-05-04 }}</ref>、2013年肯塔基打吡優勝者[[寶球|寶球]]<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.drf.com/news/hot-sire-ap-indy |title = Hot Sire: A.P. Indy |author = Patrick Reed |date = 2013-08-22 |publisher = Daily Racing Form |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-14 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180614144305/http://www.drf.com/news/hot-sire-ap-indy |archivedate = 2018-06-14 }}</ref>以及2014年肯塔基打吡及必利時錦標的優勝者{{tsl|en|California Chrome|閃亮加州}}<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/horseracing/2014/06/05/belmont-stakes-california-chrome-triple-crown-lineage-of-champions/10023763/ |title = Triple Crown hope California Chrome rarity in Sport of Kings |author = Gary Mihoces |date = 2014-06-05 |publisher = USA TODAY Sports |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-14 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180614144328/https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/horseracing/2014/06/05/belmont-stakes-california-chrome-triple-crown-lineage-of-champions/10023763/ |archivedate = 2018-06-14 }}</ref>。此外，Terlingua的兒子{{tsl|en|Storm Cat|風暴貓}}曾兩度獲評為北美著名父系馬，其後代包括曾三度獲評為北美著名父系馬的{{tsl|en|Giant's Causeway (horse)|巨人長堤}}<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.thoroughbreddailynews.com/giants-causeway-passes-away/ |title = Giant’s Causeway Passes Away |author = Alan Carasso |date = 2018-04-17 |publisher = Thoroughbred Daily News |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-14 |archive-date = 2018-06-14 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180614171358/http://www.thoroughbreddailynews.com/giants-causeway-passes-away/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>以及2015年美國三冠大賽冠軍[[美式法老_(馬)|美式法老]]的外祖父Yankee Gentleman<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/106728/triple-crown-connections |title = Triple Crown Connections |author = Avalyn Hunter |date = 2015-06-26 |publisher = Blood-Horse |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-14 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20171020135431/https://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/106728/triple-crown-connections |archivedate = 2017-10-20 }}</ref>。在秘書處的後代之間進行近親繁殖是另外一種成功且可行的方法，亦繁殖了許多分級賽錦標的優勝者，例如2004年{{tsl|en|American Champion Sprint Horse|美國最佳短途馬}}得主{{link-en|Speightstown|Speightstown (horse)}}以及2012年及2013年年度馬王{{tsl|en|Wise Dan||聰明丹}}<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/117777/inbreeding-to-secretariat-not-a-passing-fad |title = Inbreeding to Secretariat: Not a Passing Fad |author = Avalyn Hunter |date = 2013-11-01 |publisher = Blood-Horse |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-14 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170729222103/http://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/117777/inbreeding-to-secretariat-not-a-passing-fad |archivedate = 2017-07-29 }}</ref>。

秘書處在克萊伯恩農場定居後與Drone、{{tsl|en|Sir Ivor|艾驊爵士}}及{{link-en|Spectacular Bid}}這三匹種馬為鄰<ref name="NYTimes-SC@840417">{{Cite web |url = https://www.nytimes.com/1984/04/17/sports/sports-of-the-times-secretariat-at-14-is-still-a-star.html |title = Secretariat, at 14, Is Still a Star |author = Steven Crist |date = 1984-04-17 |publisher = The New York Times |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-14 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180614144335/https://www.nytimes.com/1984/04/17/sports/sports-of-the-times-secretariat-at-14-is-still-a-star.html |archivedate = 2018-06-14 }}</ref>。秘書處並沒有對Drone或艾驊爵士給予太多關注，反而牠與Spectacular Bid的關係變得友好，偶爾地會做自然的事<ref name="NYTimes-SC@840417"/><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://people.com/archive/after-15-years-of-foaling-around-superhorse-secretariat-fathers-a-big-winner-risen-star-vol-29-no-23/ |title = After 15 Years of Foaling Around, Superhorse Secretariat Fathers a Big Winner, Risen Star |author = Susan Toepfer and Bill Shaw |date = 1988-06-13 |publisher = People |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-14 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20171124014652/http://people.com/archive/after-15-years-of-foaling-around-superhorse-secretariat-fathers-a-big-winner-risen-star-vol-29-no-23/ |archivedate = 2017-11-24 }}</ref>。

== 去世 ==
在1989年秋天，19歲的秘書處被診斷患上蹄葉炎，此疾病會令牠感到痛苦，而且通常是無法治癒的<ref name="NYTimes-SC@891005">{{Cite web |url = https://www.nytimes.com/1989/10/05/sports/secretariat-racing-legend-and-fans-favorite-is-dead.html |title = Secretariat, Racing Legend And Fans' Favorite, Is Dead |author = Steven Crist |date = 1989-10-05 |publisher = The New York Times |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-15 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180615191838/https://www.nytimes.com/1989/10/05/sports/secretariat-racing-legend-and-fans-favorite-is-dead.html |archivedate = 2018-06-15 }}</ref><ref name="LAT-ME@891005">{{Cite web |url = http://articles.latimes.com/1989-10-05/sports/sp-984_1_secretariat |title = Secretariat, Suffering From Incurable Condition, Destroyed |author = Mike Embry |date = 1989-10-05 |publisher = Los Angeles Times |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-15 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161009210941/http://articles.latimes.com/1989-10-05/sports/sp-984_1_secretariat |archivedate = 2016-10-09 }}</ref>。經歷一個月的治療，秘書處的病情仍未見改善，最終牠在10月4日被[[人道毀滅|人道毀滅]]<ref name="SI-WN@900604"/><ref name="NYTimes-SC@891005"/><ref name="LAT-ME@891005"/>。克萊伯恩農場主席賽斯·漢考克（Seth Hancock）在接受訪問時形容秘書處的離世對所有員工而言是糟糕的一天<ref name="NYTimes-SC@891005"/>。秘書處死後被放入橡木棺材內並安葬於克萊伯恩農場，在其父親勇者帝王之墓的附近<ref name="LAT-ME@891005"/>。此外，傳統上勝出賽事的競賽馬在死後只會埋葬牠們的頭部、心臟及馬蹄，而秘書處則獲全屍埋葬，是一種罕見的榮譽<ref name="LM-JM@0704"/>。

在秘書處離世後，負責進行屍體解剖的獸醫是[[肯塔基大學|肯塔基大學]]首席病理學家托馬斯·索威澤克（Thomas Swerczek），他在解剖時未為秘書處心臟進行稱重，但表示：「我們都驚呆了，站在那裡一動不動。我們無法相信，秘書處的心臟很完美，並未出現任何問題。這個心臟就猶如一個巨大的引擎」<ref name="SI-WN@900604"/>。後來，索威澤克為1993年去世的另一匹競賽馬Sham進行屍體解剖，經稱重後得知Sham的心臟重量是18磅<ref>Lawrence, p. 297</ref>。基於這兩匹馬的屍體解剖結果及Sham的測量結果，索威澤克估計秘書處的心臟重量可能是22磅，而普通馬匹的心臟重量平均僅是8.5磅<ref name="SM-MO@101008">{{Cite web |url = http://www.slate.com/articles/news_and_politics/life_and_art/2010/10/why_we_love_secretariat.html |title = Why We Love Secretariat |author = Meghan O'Rourke |date = 2010-10-08 |publisher = Slate Magazine |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-15 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180615191811/http://www.slate.com/articles/news_and_politics/life_and_art/2010/10/why_we_love_secretariat.html |archivedate = 2018-06-15 }}</ref><ref name="SWM-TB@150525">{{Cite web |url = https://www.swimmingworldmagazine.com/news/the-heart-of-a-champion/ |title = The Heart of A Champion |author = Tera Bradham |date = 2015-05-25 |publisher = Swimming World Magazine |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-15 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180615193555/https://www.swimmingworldmagazine.com/news/the-heart-of-a-champion/ |archivedate = 2018-06-15 }}</ref>。

純種馬偶爾會出現擁有一個巨大的心臟的情況，而這被稱為「X因素」（X factor），是假定與遺傳條件有關並會以特定的遺傳模式傳予下一代<ref name="QRJ-MH">{{Cite journal |author = Marianna Haun |title = The X-FACTOR ~ Heart of the Matter |journal = Quarter Racing Journal |year = 1998}}</ref><ref name="RMC-MH">{{Cite book | last = Haun | first = Marianna | title = The X Factor: What it is & how to Find it : the Relationship Between Inherited Heart Size and Racing Performance | location = Neenah, WI | publisher = Russell Meerdink Company | date = 1997 | ISBN = 978-0-929346-46-5 | language = en}}</ref>。「X因素」可以追溯至一匹在歷史上著名的的競賽馬[[日蝕_(馬)|日蝕]]<ref name="QRJ-MH"/>，牠在1789年去世後被解剖，而這場解剖更被認為是英國有史以來第一次具備正式記錄的動物屍體解剖<ref name="Independent-CS@090405">{{Cite web |url = https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/books/reviews/eclipse-by-nicholas-clee-8711921.html |title = Eclipse, By Nicholas Clee |author = Charles Spencer |date = 2009-04-05 |publisher = The Independent |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-15 |archive-date = 2018-06-15 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180615214214/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/books/reviews/eclipse-by-nicholas-clee-8711921.html |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="UoC">{{Cite web |url = http://www.cam.ac.uk/research/news/solved-two-of-the-historic-riddles-of-horse-racing |title = Solved: two of the historic riddles of horse racing |author = University of Cambridge |date = 2014-06-02 |publisher = University of Cambridge |language = EN |accessdate = 2018-06-15 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170830055621/http://www.cam.ac.uk/research/news/solved-two-of-the-historic-riddles-of-horse-racing |archivedate = 2017-08-30 }}</ref>。獸醫在進行解剖工作時發現牠的心臟比其他馬匹的為大，稱重後得知其心臟的重量是14磅，幾乎是正常心臟重量的兩倍<ref name="Independent-CS@090405"/>。透過譜系研究，證實了秘書處的母系能夠追溯至日蝕的女兒，而秘書處能成為北美著名母馬的父系馬可能與「X因素」有關<ref name="QRJ-MH"/><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2007/mar/04/horseracing.features |title = Who's the daddy of them all? |author = Nicholas Clee |date = 2007-03-04 |publisher = The Guardian |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-15 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002143526/http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2007/mar/04/horseracing.features |archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>。有研究亦證明很多取得巨大成功的純種競賽馬皆擁有巨大的心臟<ref name="SWM-TB@150525"/>。

== 榮譽 ==
[[File:Secretariat_statue.jpg|thumb]]
1974年，即秘書處成為美國三冠大賽冠軍後一年，牠被選入{{tsl|en|National Museum of Racing and Hall of Fame|國家賽馬博物館及名人堂}}<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.racingmuseum.org/hall-of-fame/secretariat |title = Secretariat |author = National Museum of Racing and Hall of Fame |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-16 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180616130827/https://www.racingmuseum.org/hall-of-fame/secretariat |archivedate = 2018-06-16 }}</ref>。同年，美國商人{{tsl|en|Paul Mellon|保羅·梅隆}}委託英國雕塑家約翰·史凱平（John Skeaping）設計並製作秘書處的青銅雕像<ref name="SP-RL@100914">{{Cite web |url = https://www.sportingpost.co.za/2010/09/hooray-for-hollywood/ |title = Hooray For Hollywood |author = Robyn Louw |date = 2010-09-14 |publisher = Sporting Post |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-16 |archive-date = 2018-06-16 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180616130344/https://www.sportingpost.co.za/2010/09/hooray-for-hollywood/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>，而這個雕像有時會被人稱為「全速邁步向前的秘書處」（Secretariat in Full Stride）<ref name="NYTimes-DA@030608">{{Cite web |url = https://www.nytimes.com/2003/06/08/sports/sports-of-the-times-even-into-funny-cide-s-storied-life-rain-must-fall.html |title = Sports of The Times; Even Into Funny Cide's Storied Life, Rain Must Fall |author = Dave Anderson |date = 2003-06-08 |publisher = The New York Times |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-16 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180616132226/https://www.nytimes.com/2003/06/08/sports/sports-of-the-times-even-into-funny-cide-s-storied-life-rain-must-fall.html |archivedate = 2018-06-16 }}</ref><ref name="TRC@150104">{{Cite web |url = https://www.thoroughbredracing.com/articles/stamp-greatness-thoroughbred-legends-sculpture/ |title = The stamp of greatness: Thoroughbred legends in sculpture |author = Paul Roberts, Isabelle Taylor and Laurence Weatherly |date = 2015-01-04 |publisher = Thoroughbred Racing Commentary |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-16 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150514184353/https://www.thoroughbredracing.com/articles/stamp-greatness-thoroughbred-legends-sculpture |archivedate = 2015-05-14 }}</ref>。與實物大小一樣的青銅雕像在製成後便被安放於貝蒙園內，直至1988年才被同一雕塑家所製的複製品取代，而原本的雕像則被移至國家賽馬博物館及名人堂<ref name="TRC@150104"/>。另外，{{tsl|en|Kentucky Horse Park|肯塔基賽馬公園}}也有兩個與實物大小一樣的秘書處雕像，分別由吉姆·里諾（Jim Reno）及埃德溫·博格茨基（Edwin Bogucki）於1992年及2004年製作，展示了秘書處在不同時期的情況<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.kyhorsepark.com/equine-theme-park/park-memorials-statues/sculptures-of-the-park/ |title = SCULPTURES OF THE PARK |author = The Kentucky Horse Park |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-16 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180604154220/https://www.kyhorsepark.com/equine-theme-park/park-memorials-statues/sculptures-of-the-park/ |archivedate = 2018-06-04 }}</ref>。2015年，另一個與秘書處有關的雕像於其騎師羅恩·圖爾科特的家鄉[[加拿大|加拿大]][[新不倫瑞克省|新不倫瑞克省]]亮相，描繪了秘書處及其騎師羅恩·圖爾科特在[[貝蒙錦標|貝蒙錦標]]上越過終點線的一刻<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-brunswick/ron-turcotte-honoured-with-statue-in-grand-falls-1.3159653 |title = Ron Turcotte honoured with statue in Grand Falls |author = CBC |date = 2015-07-20 |publisher = CBC |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-16 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161228182253/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-brunswick/ron-turcotte-honoured-with-statue-in-grand-falls-1.3159653 |archivedate = 2016-12-28 }}</ref>。

1994年，體育週刊《[[運動畫刊|運動畫刊]]》將秘書處列入「過去40年最偉大的40位體育人物」排名，排行第17位<ref name="SI-WN@940919"/>。1999年，[[ESPN|ESPN]]將秘書處評為{{tsl|en|SportsCentury|20世紀最偉大的100位北美運動員}}的第35位，是名單上排名最高的三位非人類運動員之一，而其餘兩位非人類運動員皆是競賽馬，分別是排行第84位的[[鬥士_(馬)|鬥士]]及第97位的{{tsl|en|Citation (horse)|例證}}<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.espn.com/sportscentury/athletes.html |title = Top N. American athletes of the century |author = ESPN |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-16 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180513211118/https://www.espn.com/sportscentury/athletes.html |archivedate = 2018-05-13 }}</ref>。在雜誌《{{tsl|en|The Blood-Horse|純血馬 (雜誌)|純血馬}}》的{{tsl|en|Blood-Horse magazine List of the Top 100 U.S. Racehorses of the 20th Century|20世紀美國100匹頂級賽馬排名}}內，秘書處排名第二位，僅次於鬥士<ref name="Duke@p.14"/><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.nbcbayarea.com/news/sports/Horse-of-the-Century-Man-o-War-vs-Secretariat-201932431.html |title = Horse of the Century: Man o' War vs. Secretariat |author = Scott Ross |date = 2013-04-18 |publisher = National Broadcasting Company |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-16 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20171001121909/http://www.nbcbayarea.com/news/sports/Horse-of-the-Century-Man-o-War-vs-Secretariat-201932431.html |archivedate = 2017-10-01 }}</ref>。另外，為了選出20世紀最頂尖的競賽馬，《運動畫刊》在1992年委託由七名專家組成的小組進行投票，得出的結果是鬥士排名第一位而秘書處排名第二位<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.si.com/vault/issue/710861/11 |title = Then & Now 30 Years Ago 'the Best I Ever Rode' |author = William Reed |date = 1992-10-27 |publisher = Sports Illustrated |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-16 |archive-date = 2018-06-16 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180616171912/https://www.si.com/vault/issue/710861/11 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。1999年，[[美聯社|美聯社]]亦為選出20世紀最頂尖的競賽馬而委託六名專家組成小組進行投票，最終鬥士及秘書處分別排名第一及第二位，與《運動畫刊》所得的結果相同<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.espn.com/sports/horse/news/story?id=247832 |title = Man o'War voted best of 20th Century |author = ESPN |date = 1999-12-22 |publisher = The Associated Press |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-16 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20171001213155/http://www.espn.com/sports/horse/news/story?id=247832 |archivedate = 2017-10-01 }}</ref>。

1999年10月16日，在[[勒星頓_(肯塔基州)|勒星頓]]基恩蘭馬場舉行的一場儀式上，[[美國郵政署|美國郵政署]]宣佈發行印有秘書處外貌的33美分郵票<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/regal-thoroughbred-rides-into-history-when-us-postal-service-commemorates-secretariat-76669582.html |title = Regal Thoroughbred Rides Into History When U.S Postal Service Commemorates Secretariat |author = United States Postal Service |date = 1999-10-16 |publisher = PR Newswire |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-17 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180212084334/https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/regal-thoroughbred-rides-into-history-when-us-postal-service-commemorates-secretariat-76669582.html |archivedate = 2018-02-12 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.nytimes.com/aponline/2018/06/04/us/ap-rac-belmont-secretariat-anniversary.html |title = Secretariat's Mighty Ride Jolted All of Racing 45 Years Ago |author = The Associated Press |date = 2018-06-04 |publisher = The New York Times |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-17 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180617142321/https://www.nytimes.com/aponline/2018/06/04/us/ap-rac-belmont-secretariat-anniversary.html |archivedate = 2018-06-17 }}</ref><ref name="Knight@p.193">Knight, p. 193</ref>。2005年，秘書處的名字出現在ESPN Classic節目《{{tsl|en|Who's No. 1?|誰是第一}}》的其中一集《最精彩的運動表現》內，牠更是這集內唯一一位非人類運動員<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://townhall.com/tipsheet/greghengler/2010/10/05/secretariat-why-hes-one-of-espns-greatest-athletes-of-all-time-n662012 |title = Secretariat: Why He's One Of ESPN's Greatest Athletes Of All Time |author = Greg Hengler |date = 2010-10-05 |publisher = Townhall |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-17 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180617142238/https://townhall.com/tipsheet/greghengler/2010/10/05/secretariat-why-hes-one-of-espns-greatest-athletes-of-all-time-n662012 |archivedate = 2018-06-17 }}</ref>。2007年5月2日，秘書處入選{{tsl|en|Kentucky Athletic Hall of Fame|肯塔基運動員名人堂}}，是首次有動物獲得這項榮譽<ref name="Knight@p.193"/><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.americasbestracing.net/the-sport/2016-secretariat-tremendous-machine |title = Secretariat: ‘A Tremendous Machine’ |author = Tom Pedulla |date = 2016-05-18 |publisher = America's Best Racing |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-17 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180617152307/https://www.americasbestracing.net/the-sport/2016-secretariat-tremendous-machine |archivedate = 2018-06-17 }}</ref>。2013年，秘書處入選{{tsl|en|Canadian Horse Racing Hall of Fame|加拿大賽馬名人堂}}，以紀念牠在40年前的{{tsl|en|Canadian International Stakes|加拿大國際錦標}}內取得膀利<ref name="CHRHF"/>。同年，秘書處在[[Showtime電視網|Showtime]]的節目《{{tsl|en|60 Minutes Sports|六十分鐘體育}}》內亦成為節目重點<ref name="Atlantic-AC@130607"/>。而在2016年3月，秘書處勝出美國三冠大賽的畫面則成為了《運動畫刊》體壇百大時刻的第13位<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.si.com/100-greatest/?q=13-triple-triumph |title = The 100 Greatest Moments in Sports History – Triple Triumph |author = Sports Illustrated |date = 原文發表日期 |publisher = Sports Illustrated |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-17 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180617165239/https://www.si.com/100-greatest/?q=13-triple-triumph |archivedate = 2018-06-17 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.paulickreport.com/news/thoroughbred-racing/three-racing-superstars-make-sports-illustrateds-100-greatest-moments/ |title = Three Racing Superstars Make Sports Illustrated’s 100 Greatest Moments |author = Paulick Report |date = 2016-03-08 |publisher = Paulick Report |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-17 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160511211008/http://www.paulickreport.com/news/thoroughbred-racing/three-racing-superstars-make-sports-illustrateds-100-greatest-moments/ |archivedate = 2016-05-11 }}</ref>。

由於秘書處長期受到歡迎，以致潘妮·切納里在離世前仍是賽馬界的一位傑出人物，她更提倡為純種馬提供後續護理及獸醫研究<ref name="NYTimes-RG@170917"/><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/213752/bh-100-a-mighty-pair |title = BH 100: A Mighty Pair |author = Edward L. Bowen |date = 2016-07-23 |publisher = Blood-Horse |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-17 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170720195812/http://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/213752/bh-100-a-mighty-pair |archivedate = 2017-07-20 }}</ref>。2004年，一間以秘書處來命名的[[非牟利機構|非牟利機構]]「美格秘書處中心（Maker's Mark Secretariat Center）」於肯塔基賽馬公園開幕，機構致力於將退役競賽馬分類、向牠們教授新的技能並為牠們尋找新的家園<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.kentucky.com/news/business/article44486817.html |title = Retired racehorses given new life at Maker's Mark Secretariat Center |author = Tom Eblen |date = 2014-04-28 |publisher = Lexington Herald-Leader |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-17 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170918064554/http://www.kentucky.com/news/business/article44486817.html |archivedate = 2017-09-18 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.paulickreport.com/horse-care-category/secretariat-center-awarded-aspca-grant-launch-lay-component-ottbs/ |title = Secretariat Center Awarded ASPCA Grant, To Launch Lay Up Component For OTTBs |author = Paulick Report |date = 2016-08-07 |publisher = Paulick Report |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-17 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180617165147/https://www.paulickreport.com/horse-care-category/secretariat-center-awarded-aspca-grant-launch-lay-component-ottbs/ |archivedate = 2018-06-17 }}</ref>。2010年，潘妮·切納里更設立了{{tsl|en|Secretariat Vox Populi Award|秘書處人民之聲獎}}，主要頒給一些「知名度及競賽表現皆獲得美國公眾迴響，以及在純種馬賽事內得到認可」的競賽馬，並交由馬迷投票選出<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.drf.com/news/penny-chenery-creates-vox-populi-award-zenyatta-first-winner |title = Penny Chenery creates 'Vox Populi' award with Zenyatta as first winner |author = Matt Hegarty |date = 2011-01-19 |publisher = Daily Racing Form |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-17 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180617142251/http://www.drf.com/news/penny-chenery-creates-vox-populi-award-zenyatta-first-winner |archivedate = 2018-06-17 }}</ref><ref name="BH-CC@121226">{{Cite web |url = https://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/124096/paynter-to-rejoin-baffert-wins-vox-populi |title = Paynter to Rejoin Baffert, Wins Vox Populi |author = Claire Crosby |date = 2012-12-26 |publisher = Blood-Horse |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-17 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170918154813/https://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/124096/paynter-to-rejoin-baffert-wins-vox-populi |archivedate = 2017-09-18 }}</ref>。{{link-en|Paynter|Paynter (horse)}}於2012年獲頒此獎項，以表揚牠在對抗蹄葉炎時作出的努力<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.drf.com/news/paynter-named-winner-vox-populi-award |title = Paynter named winner of Vox Populi Award |author = Matt Hegarty |date = 2012-12-27 |publisher = Daily Racing Form |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-17 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160204141634/http://www.drf.com/news/paynter-named-winner-vox-populi-award |archivedate = 2016-02-04 }}</ref>。潘妮·切納里其後表示：「Paynter的受歡迎程度源於牠的戰鬥能力及令人超出預期的能力，這使牠成為最有力獲獎人選……在親眼目睹蹄葉炎的破壞性影響後，我更確信賽馬行業必須繼續勤奮地對抗這種疾病」<ref name="BH-CC@121226"/>。

秘書處的故事後來被改編為電影《{{tsl|en|Secretariat (film)|馬場奇蹟}}》，由{{tsl|en|Mike Rich|邁克·里奇}}編寫劇本、{{tsl|en|Randall Wallace|藍道爾·華萊士}}執導及[[華特迪士尼影業|華特迪士尼影業]]發行，於2010年10月8日在美國院線上映<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.nytimes.com/2010/10/03/movies/03secretariat.html?mtrref=en.wikipedia.org&gwh=137B7686143D9D84814400636CB8E9A9&gwt=pay |title = In 'Secretariat,' Horse's Owner Is the Underdog |author = John Anderson |date = 2010-10-01 |publisher = The New York Times |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-16 |archive-date = 2018-06-16 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180616130115/https://www.nytimes.com/2010/10/03/movies/03secretariat.html?mtrref=en.wikipedia.org&gwh=137B7686143D9D84814400636CB8E9A9&gwt=pay |dead-url = no }}</ref>。2020年，受到新冠病毒疫情影響，肯塔基打吡不得不延期。國家廣播公司在原肯塔基打吡播放節目加插一場由十三匹三冠馬參加虛擬肯塔基打吡，賽事由電腦模擬，結果秘書處擊敗了例證等馬奪得冠軍<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/239952/secretariat-its-his-virtual-kentucky-derby-world |title=Secretariat: It's His Virtual Kentucky Derby World |accessdate=2020-05-03 |archive-date=2020-05-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200504011042/https://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/239952/secretariat-its-his-virtual-kentucky-derby-world |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 血統 ==
秘書處的父系是{{tsl|en|Bold Ruler|勇者帝王}}。在二十世紀，勇者帝王曾八度獲評為北美著名父系馬，其獲選次數相比起其他種馬為多<ref name="SP@130509">{{Cite web |url = https://www.sportingpost.co.za/2013/05/bold-ruler-renewed/ |title = Ruler Renewed |author = Sporting Post |date = 2013-05-09 |publisher = Sporting Post |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-18 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180618175331/https://www.sportingpost.co.za/2013/05/bold-ruler-renewed/ |archivedate = 2018-06-18 }}</ref><ref name="DRF-JPS@150212">{{Cite web |url = http://www.drf.com/news/sparkman-ap-indy-carrying-bold-ruler-line |title = A.P. Indy carrying on Bold Ruler line |author = John P. Sparkman |date = 2015-02-12 |publisher = Daily Racing Form |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-18 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180618175229/http://www.drf.com/news/sparkman-ap-indy-carrying-bold-ruler-line |archivedate = 2018-06-18 }}</ref>。此外，勇者帝王更六次獲評為美國著名年輕父系馬<ref name="SP@130509"/>。儘管勇者帝王經常被歸類為一匹早熟的父系馬，而且被批評在兩歲前未有接受訓練或沒有足夠耐力，但牠有部分子嗣是錦標賽的優勝者，更有5匹子嗣勝出錦標賽三次或以上，其中包括秘書處<ref>Hunter, p. 304</ref>。1970年代，在勝出[[肯塔基打吡|肯塔基打吡]]的10匹競賽馬內，其中7匹都可追溯至勇者帝王，包括秘書處及{{tsl|en|Seattle Slew|西雅圖迴旋}}<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://kznbreeders.co.za/stallions/influential-stallions/the-great-bold-ruler/ |title = The Great Bold Ruler |author = KZN Breeders |date = 2015-09-13 |publisher = KZN Breeders |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-18 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180429024131/http://kznbreeders.co.za/stallions/influential-stallions/the-great-bold-ruler/ |archivedate = 2018-04-29 }}</ref>。

秘書處的母系是{{link-en|Somethingroyal}}。雖然Somethingroyal在出生後被投閒置散，但牠擁有出色的血統，更在1973年成為肯塔基年度母馬<ref name="McLean@p.152-153">McLean, pp. 152-153</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.drf.com/news/broodmare-year-looks-lock |title = Broodmare of the Year looks a lock |author = Lauren Stich |date = 2003-11-26 |publisher = Daily Racing Form |language = en |accessdate = 2018-06-18 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180618152249/http://www.drf.com/news/broodmare-year-looks-lock |archivedate = 2018-06-18 }}</ref>。Somethingroyal的父系是{{tsl|en|Princequillo|天子勁龍}}，牠曾八度獲評為為北美著名母馬的父系馬，而牠的子嗣亦很強壯及具備耐力<ref>McLean, p. 191</ref>。Somethingroyal的母系是{{link-en|Imperatrice}}，牠曾經勝出錦標賽，並在1947年被克里斯托弗·切納里以3萬美元購入<ref name="Capps@p.24-25">Capps, pp. 24-25</ref>。Imperatrice的子嗣有部份成為了錦標賽優勝者，有部份則成為優秀的種馬及母馬<ref name="Capps@p.24-25"/>。早在1958年，Somethingroyal已經誕下了Sir Gaylord，其後Sir Gaylord勝出錦標賽並成為了重要的種馬，子嗣包括[[葉森打吡大賽|葉森打吡大賽]]優勝者{{tsl|en|Sir Ivor|艾驊爵士}}<ref>Capps, pp. 26-27</ref>。除了Sir Gaylord，Somethingroyal的子嗣還包括First Family及Syrian Sea<ref name="McLean@p.152-153"/><ref>Capps, p. 28</ref>。

